_date\", which suggests they might want to:\n1. Count transactions per month using TRANSACTION_DATE, OR\n2. Derive a \"first transaction date\" per customer and then count customers by the month of their first transaction\n\nGiven the context and the fact that the table has CUSTOMER_NAME, the most likely interpretation is that they want to count unique customers per month based on when they made their first transaction (customer acquisition by month).\n\nHowever, this is a reasonable assumption I can make and proceed with querying. I'll ask the Cortex Analyst to count customers by the month of their first transaction date.\n"},"type":"thinking"},{"tool_use":{"client_side_execute":false,"input":{"has_time_column":true,"need_future_forecasting_data":false,"original_query":"count per month based on first_transaction_date","previous_related_tool_result_id":"","query":"Count of unique customers per month based on their first transaction date (the earliest TRANSACTION_DATE for each customer). Group by month and show the count of customers who made their first transaction in each month."},"name":"SalesSemantic","tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_019aL1hen6qqvjimGUrpLyeX","type":"cortex_analyst_text_to_sql"},"type":"tool_use"},{"tool_result":{"content":[{"json":{"query_id":"01c2c67f-0001-579f-0000-920d002e1986","result_set":{"data":[["2026-02-01","97","2026-02-01","2026-02-20","97"],["2026-01-01","249","2026-01-01","2026-01-31","249"],["2025-12-01","247","2025-12-01","2025-12-31","247"],["2025-11-01","237","2025-11-01","2025-11-30","237"],["2025-10-01","294","2025-10-01","2025-10-31","294"],["2025-09-01","279","2025-09-01","2025-09-30","279"],["2025-08-01","272","2025-08-01","2025-08-31","272"],["2025-07-01","352","2025-07-01","2025-07-31","352"],["2025-06-01","287","2025-06-01","2025-06-30","287"],["2025-05-01","320","2025-05-01","2025-05-31","320"],["2025-04-01","312","2025-04-01","2025-04-30","312"],["2025-03-01","348","2025-03-01","2025-03-31","348"],["2025-02-01","170","2025-02-08","2025-02-28","170"]],"resultSetMetaData":{"format":"jsonv2","numRows":13,"partition":0,"partitionInfo":[{"rowCount":13,"uncompressedSize":709}],"rowType":[{"length":0,"name":"MONTH","nullable":true,"precision":0,"scale":0,"type":"date"},{"length":0,"name":"UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS_COUNT","nullable":false,"precision":18,"scale":0,"type":"fixed"},{"length":0,"name":"MIN_FIRST_TRANSACTION_DATE","nullable":true,"precision":0,"scale":0,"type":"date"},{"length":0,"name":"MAX_FIRST_TRANSACTION_DATE","nullable":true,"precision":0,"scale":0,"type":"date"},{"length":0,"name":"TOTAL_FIRST_TRANSACTIONS","nullable":false,"precision":18,"scale":0,"type":"fixed"}]},"statementHandle":"01c2c67f-0001-579f-0000-920d002e1986"},"sql":"WITH __tbl_sales AS (\n  SELECT\n    customer_name,\n    transaction_date\n  FROM DEVELOPMENT.BRONZE.TBL_SALES\n), first_transaction AS (\n  SELECT\n    customer_name,\n    MIN(transaction_date) AS first_transaction_date\n  FROM __tbl_sales\n  WHERE\n    transaction_date \u003c= CURRENT_DATE\n  GROUP BY\n    customer_name\n), monthly_first_transactions AS (\n  SELECT\n    DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', first_transaction_date) AS month,\n    COUNT(customer_name) AS unique_customers_count,\n    MIN(first_transaction_date) AS min_first_transaction_date,\n    MAX(first_transaction_date) AS max_first_transaction_date,\n    COUNT(first_transaction_date) AS total_first_transactions\n  FROM first_transaction\n  GROUP BY\n    DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', first_transaction_date)\n)\nSELECT\n  month,\n  unique_customers_count,\n  min_first_transaction_date,\n  max_first_transaction_date,\n  total_first_transactions\nFROM monthly_first_transactions\nORDER BY\n  month DESC NULLS LAST\n -- Generated by Cortex Analyst (request_id: 397c4fab-463b-4a10-bc48-fc1135ec128c)\n;","text":"The question is clear and I can answer it with the following SQL."},"type":"json"}],"name":"SalesSemantic","status":"success","tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_019aL1hen6qqvjimGUrpLyeX","type":"cortex_analyst_text_to_sql"},"t