ed by Cortex Analyst (request_id: 5f03e1cb-c1cf-4a34-a33d-184ca5e85489)\n;","text":"The question is clear and I can answer it with the following SQL."},"type":"json"}],"content_index":2,"name":"SalesSemantic","sequence_number":70,"status":"success","tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01U86Snfe9VzVBdZ5e2Gu8Ai","type":"cortex_analyst_text_to_sql"}
